      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "This vehicle represents a premier opportunity to acquire a well-maintained, high-performance asset. Meticulously inspected for mechanical integrity and aesthetic consistency, it delivers a refined driving experience that exceeds standard expectations for its class. With a documented history of care and a robust powertrain, this model offers an ideal synthesis of reliability and sophistication for the discerning motorist.",
