    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Up for sale is a meticulously maintained 2018 Executive Sport Sedan in Deep Sea Blue Metallic. This vehicle has been a reliable daily driver and is in excellent mechanical health. The exterior paint retains a deep, mirror-like shine, though close inspection reveals a few minor stone chips on the front bumper and a small, superficial scratch near the rear wheel well\u2014typical for a car of this age. The interior is a highlight, featuring Oyster Dakota leather that has been treated regularly to remain soft and crack-free; it remains a smoke-free and pet-free environment. All cabin electronics, including the wide-screen navigation, dual-zone climate control, and premium surround-sound system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine is clean with no leaks, and the transmission shifts smoothly through all gears. I have a complete folder of service records showing oil changes every 5,000 miles and a recent brake pad replacement. The tires are matching Continentals with plenty of tread depth left for several seasons. This is a solid, honest car that drives as beautifully as it looks, perfect for someone seeking luxury without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 32500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
